@node What "what is ByteKiller V3.0"
@{FG fill}
ByteKiller (short: BK) is one of the Best Nuker, he allows you to nuke 
in Background, write configurable Messages and change the FileListing in 
your choosen colors.
Bk have a Port to Newfiles V3.0 so you can nuke, i.e., if you are in conf 3,
Files from conf 6 or conf 1.
Bk write only one Message for all Down-Uploads from the User.
Bk can handle Conf-Accounting and have one of the fastes routines to change
the Listing, it will only change the last bytes of your Listing.

Now BK can Handle extra Creditz for Majors, to give Uploader Creditz per 
Downloader....

BK create Datafiles for Top-Nuked User, and for later function`s, next week
all registered User gets the Bulletin-maker for this Datafiles,if you nuke 
files, and see the status from the User, you can see how many bytes and files 
you have nuked before..

@{FG Text}

This is the third big Version of ByteKiller, I hope you like it, because I
invested many Gurus and Time to make BK faster and comfortabler.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
BK is 100% new, because I must change some routines to make Bk compatible to
FAME (the New comming BBS-System), if you missing functions from the old Bk, 
please write a  Mail to me, because I don't know all previous functions.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

If you like BK or my other Tools, please call one of our DistSides to 
Register the Tools.

We sell our Registration(s) for ALL TOOLS and UPDATES for 30,-DM or 20$


@endnode


@node Why "why ByteKiller V3.0"

@{FG fill}







                This is the only one who can Handle with Fame...!


@{FG Text}
@endnode


@node notooltypes "some ToolTypes you don`t need"


@{FG fill}

 These Tooltypes are not needed, but if you have installed them, Bk use them:
@{FG Text}

NUKER.<x>=<name> :

<x>        --> @{FG fill}number, beginning from 1 to ~@{FG Text}
<name>     --> @{FG fill}name of the Nuker who have the Level to start Bk@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

PASSWORD.<x>=<password>

<x>        --> @{FG fill}the number from Nuker.<x>@{FG Text}
<password> --> @{FG fill}the Password from the Nuker@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

LOG_FILE=<path>

<path>     --> @{FG fill}Path for the Logfile from Bk@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=
@endnode
     
@node filetooltypes "Some ToolTypes you need for the FileListing "
@{FG fill}
     You need this Tooltypes to configure the Comments and the colors
     of the Comments.
     you can use Macros to add the real Nuker-Name, bytes,creditz and
     other things in the comment-line.
@{FG Text}

                          @{BG fill}@{" Important for FAME " link fametooltypes}@{BG Background}        


Macros :
~~~~~~~~

%N  @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}NukerName@{FG Text}
%U  @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}UserName@{FG Text}
%c  @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}Creditz Taken/Given@{FG Text}
%B  @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}Bytes from the Nuked File@{FG Text}

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{BG fill}SIZE.<x>=<what>@{BG Background}

<x>       @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the Number of comment 1 - ~@{FG Text}
<what>    @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the Comment for the Size @{FG Text}

IE: @{FG Highlight}@{BG Text}SIZE.1=DeleTed@{BG Background}@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@{BG fill}FAKE.<x>=<what>@{BG Background}

<x>       @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the Number of comment 1 - ~@{FG Text}
<what>    @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the Comment for the Description @{FG Text}

IE: @{FG Highlight}@{BG Text}FAKE.1=%N: Lamer, this Upload is Shit!@{BG Background}@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@{BG fill}COMMENT.<x>=<what>@{BG Background}

<x>       @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the Number of comment 1 - ~@{FG Text}
<what>    @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the Credit Comment for the Description @{FG Text}

IE: @{FG Highlight}@{BG Text}COMMENT.1=## %N: I Take you %c bytes ##@{BG Background}@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@{BG fill}FREEDOWNLOAD=<what>@{BG Background}

<what>    @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the Comment for FreeDownloads, default is "# FreeDownLoad #"@{FG Text}

IE: @{FG Highlight}@{BG Text}FREEDOWNLOAD=This File is Free@{BG Background}@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@{BG fill}FREE_COLOR=<what>@{BG Background}

what      @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the AnsiColor Numbers, default is 0@{FG Text}

IE: @{FG Highlight}@{BG Text}FREE_COLOR=44;31@{BG Background}@{FG Text}     
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@{BG fill}GIVE_COLOR=<what>@{BG Background}

what      @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the AnsiColor Numbers, default is 0@{FG Text}

IE: @{FG Highlight}@{BG Text}GIVE_COLOR=32@{BG Background}@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@{BG fill}TAKE_COLOR=<what>@{BG Background}

what      @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}the AnsiColor Numbers, default is 0@{FG Text}

IE: @{FG Highlight}@{BG Text}TAKE_COLOR=33@{BG Background}@{FG Text}     
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@{BG fill}NO_WILDCARDS@{BG Background}

@{FG fill}
This Tooltype allows to use WildCards by flagging Files...
@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@{BG fill}EXTERN_COMMENT@{BG Background}

@{FG fill}
This Tooltype allows to Write additional Comments for files, this comments
will be added on the Message...
@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@{BG fill}CREATE_FAKEFILES@{BG Background}

@{FG fill}
This Tooltype allows to create FakeFiles, if you flag File(s), and Bk doesn`t
found any, he ask you for create
@{FG Text}
=-+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+--+-=

@endnode


@node fametooltypes "ToolTypes you need for FAME" 

@{BG fill}USER_DATA=<path>@{BG Background}

path      @{BG Shine}-->@{BG Background} @{FG fill}Full Path to User.data@{FG Text}

IE: @{FG Highlight}@{BG Text}USER_DATA=BBS:User.Data@{BG Background}@{FG Text}
@endnode


@node msg "Msg-Configuration" 
@{FG fill}
Bk can write three Msg`s, you only must put these Cfg-Txtfiles in your 
ByteKiller dir :
@{FG Text}
doors:ByteKiller/Uploader.cfg
doors:ByteKiller/Award.cfg
doors:ByteKiller/Downloader.cfg
@{FG fill}
Bk can Handle some Macros in his Txt-File(s)
@{FG Text}
%N  ----> Nuker Name
%n  ----> Name from Up-Downloader
%A  ----> Name of the Nuked File(s)
%a  ----> Comments per File(s) (Additional-Comment(s))
%o  ----> Status Old Upload File(s)
%O  ----> Status Old Upload Byte(s)
%b  ----> Upload Day
%B  ----> FileSize
%t  ----> Up File(s) Taken
%T  ----> Up Bytes Taken
%g  ----> Up File(s) given
%G  ----> Up Byte(s) given
%d  ----> Down File(s) taken
%D  ----> Down Byte(s) taken
%l  ----> small List of all file(s)
%L  ----> big List of all File(s)
%s  ----> New Up-DownByte Status
%S  ----> New Up-DownFile Status


Examples :

                               @{BG fill}@{"  Award.cfg     " link msgaward}@{BG Background}
                               @{BG fill}@{"  Uploader.cfg  " link msguploader}@{BG Background}
                               @{BG fill}@{" Downloader.cfg " link msgdownloader}@{BG Background}

@endnode

@node msguploader
          ***************      Nuked File(s)     ***************

Hey %n, here is %N...
Well I could only say...

    DON'T DRINK AND TRADE!

I have *TAKEN* you %T Bytes from %O Bytes
and %t files  of %o files coz

the following Files are FAKES :

%l

and now you see what I have done per File :

%L

%a

              Please Kill this Message and don`t Reply it !

                           @{BG fill}@{" msg-Configuration " link msg}@{BG Background}

@endnode


@node msgDownloader
     *********           You`re Download-Stat-Info          *********

Hey %n , everything okay ? :) 
Well you got back %D Bytes 'coz you have
leeched files which where FAKES !
 
Here is now a list of all Fake(s)....

%L

                    !!! Please Delete This Message !!!

                           @{BG fill}@{" msg-Configuration " link msg}@{BG Background}

@endnode


@node msgaward


          ***************      BYTES GIVEN !     ***************

Hey %n, what's up Man ? 

%N  decides to give you some bytes

for your uploads...so you got %G Bytes !

here is the List of the uploaded file(s)...

%l

an here is all creditz per File....

%L


              Please Kill this Message and don`t Reply it !


                           @{BG fill}@{" msg-Configuration " link msg}@{BG Background}
@endnode

@node Start "Start ByteKiller"

ByteKiller is an XIM/FIM Door, so Please start him only from your BBS !

You can Start BK with :

"Nuke trsi*.lha Lame.txt HLM-*.dms....."

or with Flagged Files from Newfiles V3.0 !

if you start Bk, he searches first for any FakeMsg`s and if exist, asks you
if you want to nuke from this messages !

Now you can say if you want to use AutoNukeModus and if you want to have the
same options for all nuked Files.
 
All what you can do now is the same like all other Nukers, but my Nuker 
asks you if you're interested to Nuke in Background, so you can logoff or 
leech something, you don`t have to wait for the nuker until it's finished
with his work!

@endnode

